opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 14th day of June, 2012, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus and/or Extraordinary Relief and the Application for Stay are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
